{"tid":1323542,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"污名化TVB的必要性","createTime":"2019-07-16T09:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:37:47.000Z","uid":53729,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00e6c1c498bf7901eb304759e1248d1490adabea","tid":1323542,"uid":53729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"我係番工個茶水間果到仲係見到有好多人信晒TVB<br />\n<br />\n播啲野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要應對既話我地應該要俾全香港知道TVB<br />\n<br />\n有好多野都係無播，好多野都係揀黎播<br />\n所以我地應該要製造輿論，令到TVB新聞臭朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如係連儂 大大隻字寫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TVB沒有報導的真相</span><br />\n<br />\n然後係下面痴番其他媒體啲圖/文<br />\n<br />\n等啲人知道佢地係俾TVB愚弄緊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家仲有無其他建議"},{"pid":"159303f06db318a934d4d5f8a712c9972c32eb12","tid":1323542,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"做個懶人表<br />\n一次過睇哂 CCTVB 冇播而其他媒體有播的新聞<br />\n做個比較一覽表"}]}